<b>International Child Care, USA (ICC)</b> is a Christian health development agency that responds in compassion to children suffering from <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../653/30653.xml">
tuberculosis</link>, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../979/258979.xml">
malnutrition</link> and physical disabilities. Since 1967, ICC has provided vital health services, and has strengthened and empowered families and entire communities. ICC gives children in <country wordnetid="108544813" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../373/13373.xml">
Haiti</link></country>
 and the <country wordnetid="108544813" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../060/8060.xml">
Dominican Republic</link></country>
 every possible chance for a brighter and healthier future. 


